articles.title: American rescued from cave in Turkey and said to be doing well after more than a week trapped underground - CBS News
articles.description: Cave expert Mark Dickey was hit with gastric pain last weekend while helping to chart the cave system, leaving him stuck more than 3,200 feet underground.
articles.content: American explorer Mark Dickey was rescued from a cave in southern Turkey on Monday night, the Turkish Caving Federation said. Dickey "was taken out of the last exit of the cave" a little past midnigh… [+1850 chars]
